title: Evet project
author: Evet project
content: Everything is ready and the event has started! There will be 12 days to acquire evet points (check the points table on discord or evet.ink). Each purchase you make must be registered in the form where several addresses (BTC, ETH and BNB) will appear so that you can choose the payment method. You must include your discord username, the tx, and the amount of money.Links of interest for the launch event:Evet Webpage: https://evet.ink/Launch Event Info: https://evet.ink/?page_id=818Ranking Contributors: https://evet.ink/?page_id=855Contributors Form: https://evet.ink/?page_id=885Discord: https://discord.gg/XSvuBFGc**Users who participate in the testnet but do not buy points will not be able to apply the multiplier for participating. It is mandatory to have points to apply the multipliers!!TOP 3 users with more points will obtain a PoS blockchain FOR FREE!We are now listed on Pecunia!
